Given - I am logged in
And I am on the Page 8 of Cranial MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Brainstem' from the dropdown

And 'I describe' button is selected
And 'I know' button is enabled 
And 'Mesencephalon' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Pon' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Medulla oblongata' checkbox is enabled 

When I select 'Mesencephalon' checkbox
Then 'Crus cerebri' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Tegmentum mesencephali' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Lamina tecti' checkbox is enabled 

When I select 'Crus cerebri' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled 

When I select 'Right' checkbox 
Then checkbox is selected
When I select 'Left' checkbox 
Then checkbox is selected

When I select 'Tegmentum mesencephali' checkbox
Then 'Substantia nigra' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Nucleus ruber' checkbox is enabled 

When I select 'Substantia nigra' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected 
When I select 'Nucleus ruber' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected 

When I select 'Lamina tecti' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected 

When I select 'Pon' checkbox 
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Central' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Peripheral' checkbox is enabled 

When I select 'Right' checkbox 
Then checkbox is selected 
When I select 'Left' checkbox 
Then checkbox is selected 
When I select 'Central' checkbox 
Then checkbox is selected 
When I select 'Peripheral' checkbox 
Then checkbox is selected 

When I select ''Medulla oblongata' checkbox
Then 'Anterior' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Central' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Posterior' checkbox is enabled 

When I select 'Anterior' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected 
When I select 'Central' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected 
When I select 'Posterior' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected 

























 